<D>__{we found a body out by the army base yesterday. been there for a long time.}
<A>__{hollis squints at a rubber lure, rejects it }
<C>__{hollis}
<D>__{was it davy crockett or jim bowie?}
<C>__{sam}
<P>__{(smiles)}
<D>__{you recall if charley wade was a mason?}
