<D>__{charley? i believe he was. used to go for lodge meetings over to laredo. what's he got to do with your body?}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{all it was wearing was a big old masonic ring and a rio county sheriffs badge.}
<A>__{hollis reacts. sam puts a foot on the gunwale of the boat.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{you don't remember anything else from that last night you saw him, do you?}
<C>__{hollis}
